{"tid":353924,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"動畫《伊藤潤二傑作集》1月放送","createTime":"2017-08-10T04:20:27.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-12T03:05:58.000Z","uid":45373,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c877993c1af2ea5f6b5b2c9885af0d3ac9da54fa","tid":353924,"uid":45373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T04:20:27.000Z","msg":"先日アニメ化を発表した伊藤潤二作品ですが、『伊藤潤二傑作集』を原作として、2018年冬よりテレビアニメとして放送されることが決定いたしました。監督・キャラクターデザインは『DIABOLIK LOVERS（第一期）』で監督を務めた田頭しのぶさん。<br />\n伊藤潤二アニメプロジェクトのティザーサイトも、2017年8月10日の丑三つ時（2時22分）にオープンしました。<br />\n【スタッフ】<br />\n原作：伊藤潤二『伊藤潤二傑作集』『魔の断片』（朝日新聞出版刊）<br />\n監督・キャラクターデザイン：田頭しのぶ<br />\nアニメーション制作：スタジオディーン<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/10/121939_7f8f549b3a4f08173ff3f3e2dd1296cd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F10%2F121939_7f8f549b3a4f08173ff3f3e2dd1296cd.jpg&h=b32236f2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n好似無乜印象之前有出過動畫"},{"pid":"1880e63155165f8cac59f1ec051bf3ba8c3a396c","tid":353924,"uid":10292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T04:21:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"801d98df840e7189302b14d030e065de0efb9f57","tid":353924,"uid":130162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T04:22:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6f19b261be995b58831754c80a1f188e4ec2914","tid":353924,"uid":45373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T04:23:37.000Z","msg":"魚 好似有出過動畫電影 不過聽聞好似好垃圾"},{"pid":"18914670031387178f53412dfc1307d00271bce4","tid":353924,"uid":2386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T05:51:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>魚 好似有出過動畫電影 不過聽聞好似好垃圾</blockquote><br />\n改晒劇情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dea